overview: Jake Johannsen -- who has appeared on "The Late Show with David Letterman" more times than any other stand-up comedian -- offers his quirky perspective on taxes, relationships, fatherhood and more in this hilarious performance. Topics include Johannsen's story of falling in love and getting married, his theory that taxes are a ruse to imprison everyone and the things his 5-year-old daughter knows that bewilder him.
title: Jake Johannsen: I Love You
